        "TileImage": "$($repository d4afe9b1-8e6d-4e2d-83a7-58b78312ccbd).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. Our client is Google. They are mad that not everyone is using their search engine and have identified 3 individuals who use the DuckDuckGo search engine instead. They have asked us to eliminate them, preferably using explosive ducks, in order to additionally ruin DuckDuckGo&apos;s reputation.",
